Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.24,0:05:03.16,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}來吧 大鬧一場囉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.16,0:05:04.91,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}可別怪我不客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.91,0:05:06.87,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}瞄準未來
